reviewText: This was a gift to my auntie & she was very excited to receive it.  The seller was just fine, quality good, shipping on time.

This is a comedy film starring 2 icons of Mexican cinema Jorge Negrete and Lus Aguilar, and they play the roll of single men that look for women for fun, but in this fun life they be introduced 2 beautiful girls that change them and got for next an top important goal marriege with them.
